          <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Invest in America Act of 2015 </strong></p> <p>This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code to modify the formula for calculating the tax on the net capital gains of individual taxpayers to provide for a maximum 15% rate on the adjusted net capital gain of such taxpayers. </p>]]></text>
